Adrian Rawlins https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Adrian_Rawlins 0 Adrian Justin Rawlins (born 27 March 1958) is an English actor who is probably best known for playing Arthur Kidd in The Woman in Black (1989) and James Potter in the Harry Potter films.
